In addition, as following the recommendation did by @petebacondarwin in https://github.com/angular/angular.js/issues/10007#issuecomment-168425866 it is able to assign it to any value, event enclosing controller. Ex:

```html
<toggle as='$ctrl.myToggle'></toggle>
```

